      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently requires significant mechanical attention to be roadworthy, including engine work and a suspension overhaul. The exterior has substantial body damage, including rusted panels and peeling clear coat, while the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This would be an ideal candidate for a dedicated parts car or a complete ground-up restoration for an experienced mechanic.",
