    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to an exacting, showroom standard. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a motorcar in pristine condition, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior entirely devoid of wear. Every mechanical system has been rigorously vetted to ensure it meets the highest performance benchmarks. Designed for the discerning enthusiast who demands a vehicle indistinguishable from new.",
