    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen is mechanically flawless, boasting a documented 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance is complete: the dual-VANOS system has been rebuilt with uprated components, rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. The chassis remains taut with no bushing play, and the original Alpine White paint retains its deep luster over a concours-level interior. This is a turn-key enthusiast example with a zero-fault DME and meticulous service provenance.",
